name: Felly - No Tears Left To Cry

metadata.description: No tears left to cry is the most recent recording from the Bad Radio album that just dropped a few weeks ago.  It's inspired by a lot of the older music I used to listen to and has a lot of organica within it.  The drums are recorded to tape as well as the acoustic guitars.  Originally I thought this record would be for something to come in the future but it helped bring life to the album as it needed something with driving drums.  I hope you enjoy and thank you all for supporting me on here.  Tour coming in April.  Love
metadata.name: No Tears Left To Cry #1
